                            Hello Dr <%= name %> <br> <span style="font-size:18px"> Welcome to Medlog</span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>



        <div class="container" style="position: absolute;margin-top: 5em;margin-left: 0.7em; width: 60em;height: 20em;left: 333px;top: 112px;border: 3px solid #006798;box-sizing: border-box;border-radius: 10px;background-color: white;">
