                font-family: Roboto;
                font-style: normal;
                font-weight: normal;
                font-size: 21px;
                line-height: 19px;
                color: #4e4e4e;">
                  <td style="padding-right: 5em; padding-top: 1.5em; padding-left: 2em;">•Clinic / Hospital</td>
